Individual




Jay L. Geldmacher



Mr. Jay L. Geldmacher is President & Chief Executive Officer at Artesyn Embedded Technologies, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Seagate Technology Plc, Seagate Technology LLC and Eller College of Management. Mr. Geldmacher was previously employed as an Independent Director by Owens-Illinois, Inc., President & Group Vice President by Emerson Network Power-Embedded Computing, Inc., President by Astec Power Solutions, Executive Vice President by Emerson Electric Co., and Executive Vice President by Knowles Electronics Holdings, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Arizona and an MBA from The University of Chicago.



